b. Automatically Collected Data:
We may automatically collect certain technical data when you use the App, including:

Device information (model, OS version)

IP address and geolocation data

Usage data (pages visited, clicks, time spent)

Crash reports and diagnostics

2. How We Use Your Information
We use the collected data to:

Process and fulfill your orders

Communicate important updates about your account and orders

Personalize your shopping experience and recommendations

Improve and optimize our App performance and services

Detect, prevent, and respond to fraud or other security risks

Comply with legal and regulatory obligations

3. Data Sharing and Disclosure
We do not sell or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share your data only as necessary for:

Service providers who assist with payment processing, delivery, customer support, and IT services (under strict confidentiality agreements)

Legal requests or to comply with law enforcement, courts, or regulatory authorities

Protecting our rights, property, or safety, or that of our users and the public

4. Data Security
We employ industry-standard security measures including encryption, firewalls, and secure cloud storage to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. However, no method of transmission or storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

5. Your Rights and Choices
You have the right to:

Access and review your personal data held by us

Correct inaccurate or incomplete information

Request deletion of your data, subject to legal or operational restrictions

Opt-out of marketing communications

To exercise these rights, please contact us using the details below.

6. Data Retention
We retain your personal information only as long as necessary to provide services, comply with legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce agreements.

7. Children‚Äôs Privacy
